### Get all tasks
GET https://localhost:7000/api/usertasks
Accept: application/json

### Get all tags
GET https://localhost:7000/api/tags
Accept: application/json

### Get tasks with multiple tags
GET https://localhost:7000/api/usertasks/with-multiple-tags
Accept: application/json

### Create a new tag
POST https://localhost:7000/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Testing",
  "description": "Testing related tasks"
}

### Create a new task
POST https://localhost:7000/api/usertasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Task",
  "description": "This is a test task created via API",
  "dueDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "priority": 2,
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "telephone": "+1-555-9999",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "tagIds": [1, 2]
}

### Get task by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/usertasks/1
Accept: application/json

### Update task
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/usertasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "dueDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "priority": 3,
  "fullName": "Updated User",
  "telephone": "+1-555-8888",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "tagIds": [1, 3]
}

### Delete task
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/usertasks/1